{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/GetStarted"},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Package-installation","text":"Package installation","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To use EUDI Wallet Kit, add the following dependency to your Package.swift:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["dependencies: [","\t\t.package(url: \"https:\/\/github.com\/eu-digital-identity-wallet\/eudi-lib-ios-wallet-kit.git\", .upToNextMajor(from: \"0.6.6\"))","]"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then add the Eudi Wallet package to your target’s dependencies:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["dependencies: [","\t\t.product(name: \"EudiWalletKit\", package: \"eudi-lib-ios-wallet-kit\"),","]"]},{"text":"Initialization","type":"heading","anchor":"Initialization","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/EudiWallet","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" class provides a unified API for the two user attestation presentation flows. It is initialized with a document storage manager instance. For SwiftUI apps, the wallet instance can be added as an ","type":"text"},{"code":"environmentObject","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to be accessible from all views. A KeyChain implementation of document storage is available.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\tlet certificates = [\"pidissuerca02_cz\", \"pidissuerca02_ee\", \"pidissuerca02_eu\", \"pidissuerca02_lu\", \"pidissuerca02_nl\", \"pidissuerca02_pt\", \"pidissuerca02_ut\"]","    wallet = try! EudiWallet(serviceName: \"my_wallet_app\", trustedReaderCertificates: certificates.map { Data(name: $0, ext: \"der\")! }, logFileName: \"temp.txt\")","    wallet.userAuthenticationRequired = true","    wallet.openID4VpConfig = OpenId4VpConfiguration(clientIdSchemes: [.x509SanDns, .x509Hash])","    wallet.transactionLogger = MyFileTransactionLogger(wallet: wallet)","\twallet.loadAllDocuments()"]},{"text":"BLE Transfer Mode","type":"heading","anchor":"BLE-Transfer-Mode","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/EudiWallet\/bleTransferMode","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" property controls the Bluetooth Low Energy role used during proximity (ISO 18013-5) presentation."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You can set it during initialization via "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/EudiWalletConfiguration\/bleTransferMode","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or update it later on the wallet instance:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"code":".server","type":"codeVoice"}]},{"type":"text","text":" (default): The holder device acts as a GATT peripheral (server), advertising and waiting for the reader to connect."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":".client","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": The holder device acts as a GATT central (client), scanning and connecting to the reader’s peripheral.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"code":".both","type":"codeVoice"}]},{"type":"text","text":": The holder device supports both modes simultaneously and advertises both in the QR device engagement."}]}]}]},{"code":["let config = EudiWalletConfiguration(","    serviceName: \"my_wallet_app\",","    trustedReaderCertificates: [Data(name: \"eudi_pid_issuer_ut\", ext: \"der\")!],","    bleTransferMode: .server  \/\/ default; use .client or .both as needed",")","let wallet = try! EudiWallet(eudiWalletConfig: config)","wallet.bleTransferMode = .client"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"OpenID4VCI-Configuration","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"OpenID4VCI Configuration"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The wallet now supports multiple OpenID4VCI issuer configurations for enhanced flexibility. You can configure the wallet with a dictionary of issuer configurations:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Configure multiple OpenID4VCI issuers with DPoP support","let issuerConfigurations: [String: OpenId4VciConfiguration] = [","    \"eudi_pid_issuer\": OpenId4VciConfiguration(","        credentialIssuerURL: \"https:\/\/pid.issuer.example.com\",","        requireDpop: true,","        issuerMetadataPolicy: .requireSigned,","        dpopKeyOptions: KeyOptions(","            secureAreaName: \"SecureEnclave\", curve: .P256, accessControl: .requireUserPresence","        )","    ),","    \"mdl_issuer\": OpenId4VciConfiguration(","        credentialIssuerURL: \"https:\/\/mdl.issuer.example.com\",","        requireDpop: false,","        issuerMetadataPolicy: .ignoreSigned","    )","]","","\/\/ Register additional issuers after initialization","try wallet.registerOpenId4VciServices(issuerConfigurations)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"code":"issuerMetadataPolicy","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to control signed metadata handling per issuer:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":".requireSigned"},{"type":"text","text":" for issuers that require signed metadata validation"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":".ignoreSigned"},{"text":" for environments that still use unsigned metadata","type":"text"}]}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/eudiwalletkit\/getstarted"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit"]]},"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"How to install and initialize EUDI Wallet Kit in your project"}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"role":"article","modules":[{"name":"EudiWalletKit"}],"roleHeading":"Article","title":"Get started"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Essentials","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/ManageDocuments","doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/SecureAreas","doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/PresentationService","doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/WalletUI"],"anchor":"Essentials"}],"references":{"doc://EudiWalletKit/documentation/EudiWalletKit/EudiWallet/bleTransferMode":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/EudiWallet\/bleTransferMode","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Ble transfer mode"}],"url":"\/documentation\/eudiwalletkit\/eudiwallet\/bletransfermode","title":"bleTransferMode","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"bleTransferMode"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"BleTransferMode","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:21MdocDataTransfer1801315BleTransferModeO"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://EudiWalletKit/documentation/EudiWalletKit":{"url":"\/documentation\/eudiwalletkit","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit","title":"EudiWalletKit","abstract":[{"text":"EUDI Wallet Kit library for iOS","type":"text"}],"role":"collection"},"doc://EudiWalletKit/documentation/EudiWalletKit/WalletUI":{"abstract":[],"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/eudiwalletkit\/walletui","title":"EUDI iOS Wallet reference implementation","type":"topic","role":"sampleCode","identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/WalletUI"},"doc://EudiWalletKit/documentation/EudiWalletKit/PresentationService":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/eudiwalletkit\/presentationservice","title":"PresentationService","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/PresentationService","abstract":[{"text":"Presentation service abstract protocol","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PresentationService"}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"PresentationService","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://EudiWalletKit/documentation/EudiWalletKit/EudiWallet":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"User wallet implementation"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"EudiWallet"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"EudiWallet"}],"title":"EudiWallet","url":"\/documentation\/eudiwalletkit\/eudiwallet","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/EudiWallet"},"doc://EudiWalletKit/documentation/EudiWalletKit/SecureAreas":{"url":"\/documentation\/eudiwalletkit\/secureareas","type":"topic","kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/SecureAreas","title":"Custom key management","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Eudi Wallet Kit supports custom key management through the implementation of SecureArea and SecureKeyStorage protocols. This document details the process of integrating custom key management with the library."}],"role":"article"},"doc://EudiWalletKit/documentation/EudiWalletKit/EudiWalletConfiguration/bleTransferMode":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/EudiWalletConfiguration\/bleTransferMode","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"BLE transfer mode for proximity presentation. Controls the role the device plays during BLE data transfer."}],"url":"\/documentation\/eudiwallet